data.description: This home features a spacious 3 bedroom, 3 bath ranch in the Cascade Heights sought after area. It has a full finished basement with fireplace.  Original hardwood floors a fenced backyard. Great location as it is an easy access to 285 and just miles away from Camp Creek Marketplace, Shopping, Movie Theatre & More. It also minutes away to the Airport. Sold as-is. This home is a must see!!
